---
name: cljs.core/*print-newline*
see also:
---

## Summary

Set to false by [doc:cljs.core/enable-console-print!] to prevent
[doc:cljs.core/println] and [doc:cljs.core/prn] from duplicating the newline
already appended by JavaScript console.
